Package com.ephesoft.gxt.core.client.i18n

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoreCommonConstants
    The CoreCommonConstants is an interface for constants common to whole application UI.
    CustomWorkflowConstants
    The interface is used to define all the constants used in the Custom Workflow page and support internationalization.
    CustomWorkflowMessages
    The interface is used to define all the messages used in the Custom Workflow page and support internationalization.
    FolderManagementConstants
    The interface is used to define all the constants used in the Folder Management page and support internationalization.
    FolderManagementMessages
    The interface is used to define all the messages used in the Folder Managgement page and support internationalization.
    LocaleCommonConstants
    The LocaleCommonConstants is an interface for declaring the keys mapping with the locale for constants common to whole application UI.
    LocaleCommonMessages
    The LocaleCommonMessages is an interface for declaring the keys mapping with the locale for messages common to whole application UI.
    ThemeMessages
    The class is used to define all the messages used in the Theme module and support internationalization.
    UploadBatchConstants
    The class is used to define all the constants used in the Upload Batch module and support internationalization.
    UploadBatchMessages
    The class is used to define all the messages used in the Upload Batch module and support internationalization.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatchClassConstants
    The interface is used to define all the constants used in the Batch Class UI and support internationalization.
    BatchClassMessages
    The interface is used to define all the messages used in the Batch Class UI and support internationalization.
    CommonLocaleInfo
    CommonLocaleInfo holds the list of all the constant and messages which are used all over screens.
    LocaleConstants  
    LocaleDictionary
    The dictionary which stores all the locale information with respect to application level and screen specific locales.
    LocaleInfo
    The locale information specific to each screen(module).
    LocaleMessages  
    SystemConfigConstants
    The class is used to define all the constants used in the system config page and support internationalization.
    SystemConfigMessages
    The class is used to define all the messages used in the system config page and support internationalisation.
    ThemeConstants
    The class is used to define all the constants used in the Theme module and support internationalization.
